description: Used to cancel an open change request. Must be sent before the status of the request changes to APPLYING, the final stage of completing your change request. You can describe a change during the 60-day request history retention period for API calls.

parameters.name: Catalog
parameters.description: Required. The catalog related to the request. Fixed value: AWSMarketplace.

parameters.name: ChangeSetId
parameters.description: Required. The unique identifier of the StartChangeSet request that you want to cancel.

nested_items.name: ChangeSetId
nested_items.description: The unique identifier for the change set referenced in this request.

nested_items.name: ChangeSetArn
nested_items.description: The ARN associated with the change set referenced in this request.
